{
  "stem": "11801.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Personally, I was, at 16, probably looked like an 11-year-old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it's, it never, it was never a problem with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, we knew that the English were coming, that the English liberated Brussels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I can only describe it as a tidal wave of we all-- all the children, all those who could walk, we all left.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We all-- the children and, and the adults, I think, everybody just went downtown to see the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was, you know, an exhilarating experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they came in on their tanks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I, I only remember the tanks, you know, coming in through the main street, and the soldiers throwing candies and chewing gum, which I had never seen-- chocolate bars, oranges, I mean, things that we hadn't seen in years.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So this-- it, it was magic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was sheer magic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "For me, of course, it was a great relief.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I no-- [CRYING] I no longer had fear, you know, of being discovered and, and endangering the, the entire orphanage.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And we-- on, on the way downtown, which may have been a-- it was quite a long walk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we ran.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It, it was just-- there was no holding anyone back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We saw many discarded German uniforms on the street, which was rather interesting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We saw, I guess what used to be German buildings, being, being raided, which perhaps, was not so nice, but was understandable.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, everything was taken out, because the shortages in all of Europe, including Belgium, were absolutely horrendous.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, for about two years, I think, we wore wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because there were no shoes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, and children's feet grow.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
